  <lyrics>[V1]
 Tukuy kayniyta Jaywaspa chimpaykamuyki Señorniy
 Tukuy sonqoy Qanllataña, sirvisuyta munani
 
[C]
 Chimpakamuyki, chakisniykiman;
 Noqamanta imatapis, ruway Señorniy.
 
[V2]
 K’umuykamusojkunata uyarinki Qan Diosniy
 Qhuyawaspa kallpachaway Santo Espirituykiwan.
 
[V3]
 Qhespichiway juchasniyta, may chhikachus kasqanta.
 Juchasniyta wijch'uspataj, sirvisuyta atisaj.
 
[V4]
 Takillasajpuni Qanman sonqoyman jamuwajta
 Diospaj allinta kawsaspa, Jesusmanta willasaj.
 
[V5]
 Almay junfa kusikuywan, Qampata kasqaymanta.
 Ñapis cielo wasiypeqa, kawsamusajña Señor.
 
</lyrics></song>